Bangalore,The Organic World - Cunningham Road,"Shah Sultan Complex, Cunningham Rd, Vasanth Nagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560001","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+Cunningham+Road/@12.986871,77.594783,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae17d8a4b42981:0x5be2aa72d46ad7f0!8m2!3d12.986871!4d77.594783!16s%2Fg%2F11fktdq9n0",4.3,0,Im Fleur,4.0,3 years ago,1,Response from the owner 3 years ago Hi Im Fleur. Thank you for shopping at The Organic World. We are delighted that you enjoyed the experience! Customer satisfaction remains at the heart of our endeavour and we are so glad that we could meet your expectations. Your heartfelt … More,"Love this store 🥰. It offers an array of fresh, locally sourced produce that are reasonably (and transparently!) priced. The shop is always clean, the patient staff don't seem to mind how long I wander back and forth the aisles examining 🧐 and exploring 👣, and their rustic display satisfies even the odd closet OCD-personalities. Aside from fruits and vegetables, I'd highly recommend their 🥭 jam and 🍋 curd, detox teas and local snacks (who could resist spicy murukku?!) that are worth the efforts in bringing home as souvenirs! The store also offers speciality items less common available in supermarkets such as protein shakes and sauerkraut. This shop is also a hidden gem for spices, flours, skincare, home-wares and unique gifts. It is almost impossible to walk out empty handed. The store offers eco-bags for your shopping and accepts NFC!",2026-05-09 13:09:05
