Bangalore,The Organic World - HRBR Layout,"708, 3rd Cross Rd, HRBR Layout 1st Block, HRBR Layout, Kalyan Nagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560043","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HRBR+Layout/@13.0175162,77.6442832,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae17d70c577cf3:0x7e4a70bc35aa1a4e!8m2!3d13.0175162!4d77.6442832!16s%2Fg%2F11p5y5vjht",4.3,0,,,,0,,"I have been a loyal customer at this outlet of Organic World almost ever since they opened it. I generally find good in everything even when it is in the dumps. However, in this case I am forced to bring out the callous attitude of the management of Organic World. there are two aspects to this business. Customer service and Products provided. Customer service is excellent. The staff members are super responsive and helpful. They go out of their way both in-store and home delivery. I give them 10/10. As far as products are concerned the company's performance is worse than pathetic. They stock grocery almost close to the expiry. They have gradually cut down on multi-brand grocery and pushed their own brand (Wellbe). Even their own brand Wellbe products are old vus a vis the packed date.. They don't care about the age of the grocery of Wellbe brand itself. I have provided my feedback time and time again to various company reps. All my appeals for fresh and wider variety of brands has simply fallen on deaf ears. Everyone from the management try their best to convince me as to why they stock old grocery. Does any customer prefer older packets versus the fresh ones in grocery? I get a strong hunch that either they are on the way to close down their business or they are making too much of profits that they don't care about losing customers. Even after my similar review months back, I am yet see any serious effort to manage their procurement. I used to buy almost all grocery, veggies, dairy, etc from this store until recently. Today I visited another store as I didn't find the grocery I wanted. Now, I visit them for minimal shopping simply because of the ever pleasant staff members at the store. Good luck!",2026-05-11 01:41:38
Bangalore,The Organic World - HRBR Layout,"708, 3rd Cross Rd, HRBR Layout 1st Block, HRBR Layout, Kalyan Nagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560043","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HRBR+Layout/@13.0175162,77.6442832,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae17d70c577cf3:0x7e4a70bc35aa1a4e!8m2!3d13.0175162!4d77.6442832!16s%2Fg%2F11p5y5vjht",4.3,0,,,,0,,"We went to check out this store today - as we’ve been to another one across the street. We needed a tooth brush - we asked the people work there , the guy we have no idea what’s the materials but I can find out from my manager in two minutes!! - he went out of the store and checking his phone and ignored us completely. Surprised to see the poor customer service - across the street the organic store they took care of us. Just a note to the owner - store was so hot , all the oils were melted and warm. I don’t usually give 1 star rating but the worker ignored us. Too bad the store had good organic stuff. Hopefully will get better. Cheers.",2026-05-11 01:41:38
