Bangalore,The Organic World - HRBR Layout,"708, 3rd Cross Rd, HRBR Layout 1st Block, HRBR Layout, Kalyan Nagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560043","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HRBR+Layout/@13.0175162,77.6442832,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae17d70c577cf3:0x7e4a70bc35aa1a4e!8m2!3d13.0175162!4d77.6442832!16s%2Fg%2F11p5y5vjht",4.3,0,,,,0,,"I've been a loyal customer of Organic World for over 6-7 years, and I must say, it's an exceptional store! The manager, Mr. Ravikumar, is truly awesome - extremely helpful, patient, and knowledgeable. What's more, we share a common hometown, Kodagu , which has created a special bond between us. Mr. Ravikumar has become more of a friend than just a store manager. He always recommends new and exciting products, ensuring I'm up-to-date on the best offerings. Kudos to Organic World and Mr. Ravikumar for an outstanding shopping experience!",2026-05-11 01:41:54
Bangalore,The Organic World - HRBR Layout,"708, 3rd Cross Rd, HRBR Layout 1st Block, HRBR Layout, Kalyan Nagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560043","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HRBR+Layout/@13.0175162,77.6442832,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae17d70c577cf3:0x7e4a70bc35aa1a4e!8m2!3d13.0175162!4d77.6442832!16s%2Fg%2F11p5y5vjht",4.3,0,,,,0,,"""I've been to this store over 1000 times, but my last visit was a real letdown. The checkout line was a nightmare - I waited 15 minutes just to pay! The staff seemed completely unbothered, chatting with each other instead of helping customers. To make matters worse, it took multiple employees to ring up my items, and even then, it was a struggle. When I asked to speak to the manager, I was told they were out. It's clear that the staff's behavior changes when the boss isn't around. I want to remind the staff that customers like me aren't looking for freebies or special treatment. We just expect basic respect and courtesy, especially when we're paying for services. A little humanity and kindness go a long way. I hope the staff will take my feedback to heart and improve their customer service skills.",2026-05-11 01:41:54
