Bangalore,The Organic World - HSR Layout,"483, 17th Cross, 27th Main Rd, opposite Nift, Sector 2, HSR Layout, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560102","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HSR+Layout/@12.9116583,77.651559,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae150352a71849:0x3f30193045cebf5a!8m2!3d12.9116583!4d77.651559!16s%2Fg%2F11grqgf_0c",4.2,0,,,,0,,"The place is good for buying organic products and vegetables too. Stuffs are also good and helpful in nature. But my last 2 visits change my thoughts about their trustworthiness. They billed me with extra items which I did not bought or with the increase quantity of items. And this happened 2 times in series. After paying the amount when I checked the bill I found those and told them. They are like “oh sorry sir, system problem.” And they refunded that extra money too. But this should not happen almost eveytime. So for all the buyers, please check the charged amount and bill before leaving the store in case if you don’t check the bill everytime. And for owner, please install a screen mirroring the billing screen so that buyers also can see what items the cashiers are adding. And if you don’t that means you don’t care about your consumers or buyers.",2026-05-11 17:18:02
