Bangalore,The Organic World - HSR Layout,"483, 17th Cross, 27th Main Rd, opposite Nift, Sector 2, HSR Layout, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560102","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HSR+Layout/@12.9116583,77.651559,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae150352a71849:0x3f30193045cebf5a!8m2!3d12.9116583!4d77.651559!16s%2Fg%2F11grqgf_0c",4.2,0,,,,0,,"Horrible experience. Purchased a few products and realised one of it was near expiry once reaching home. Had to go back and exchange, but they didn’t have stock for the same product and asked me to come back on Monday. Secondly, there were 2 products of the same variant priced differently. One was 59/- and the other was 149/-. The staff I spoke to had nothing to tell me and didn’t even listen to me half of the time. Before adorning hefty claims I would suggest the team at the organic world to have basic processes in place before displaying products on the shelf. I literally stormed off the shop being absolutely disappointed in the staff and the treatment that I received, but no one did anything. You will definitely disappoint and probably lose a few more customers if these things are not looked into.",2026-05-11 17:18:21
