Bangalore,The Organic World - HSR Layout,"483, 17th Cross, 27th Main Rd, opposite Nift, Sector 2, HSR Layout, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560102","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HSR+Layout/@12.9116583,77.651559,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae150352a71849:0x3f30193045cebf5a!8m2!3d12.9116583!4d77.651559!16s%2Fg%2F11grqgf_0c",4.2,0,,,,0,,"The Organic World is known for hosting all sorts of organic consumables under one roof. You get fruits & vegetables, dairy, staples (including cold pressed oils), personal care products, kitchen ware, organic clothing et al in one store. The Organic personal care products collection here is pretty impressive. It's competitive enough for the popular home delivery apps that we use. I could easily spot more than 5 or 6 organic brands in this category and that itself is quite a number. Also, the potted plants collection is very nice. These are indoor plants in beautiful ceramic planters that are ready to gift. The store also keeps a nice range of cast iron and terracotta cooking vessels besides many brass and terracotta water 'reusable' bottles. Anything and everything here is chemical free or 'eco friendly'. There're many organic chocolate brands here too along with energy bars in various flavors as well. Overall a great store where you can find most organic products and brands.",2026-05-11 17:18:42
