Bangalore,The Organic World - HSR Layout,"483, 17th Cross, 27th Main Rd, opposite Nift, Sector 2, HSR Layout, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560102","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HSR+Layout/@12.9116583,77.651559,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae150352a71849:0x3f30193045cebf5a!8m2!3d12.9116583!4d77.651559!16s%2Fg%2F11grqgf_0c",4.2,0,,,,0,,"I have previously visited the store and placed an order for ghee. They took advance from me as they told me that they need money to place an order from the vendors. I trusted them , payed, gave my plastic container and placed a home delivery. The staff member lost my container and also gave the ghee after 2 weeks, that too I went to the store and collected it. They didn't bother delivering it even though they had the ghee stock. Do not trust the people for home delivery . Their ghee is good, no doubt. But the staff members are not professional at all. They play around and joke when there are customers and do not attend properly. Do not pay any advance as they will deliver on their own terms. I'd suggest not to place an online order either but go to the store and purchase if the ghee is available. I like the place but please change your staff members as they're not professional.",2026-05-11 17:18:51
