Bangalore,The Organic World - HSR Layout,"483, 17th Cross, 27th Main Rd, opposite Nift, Sector 2, HSR Layout, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560102","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HSR+Layout/@12.9116583,77.651559,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae150352a71849:0x3f30193045cebf5a!8m2!3d12.9116583!4d77.651559!16s%2Fg%2F11grqgf_0c",4.2,0,Parvathy E,5.0,6 years ago,0,Response from the owner 6 years ago Thanks Nandini ! Let’s talk about why organic is expensive whenever you come around next,Expensive. But very well kept store. Good range of products. Zero waste.,2026-05-11 17:19:11
Bangalore,The Organic World - HSR Layout,"483, 17th Cross, 27th Main Rd, opposite Nift, Sector 2, HSR Layout, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560102","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+HSR+Layout/@12.9116583,77.651559,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae150352a71849:0x3f30193045cebf5a!8m2!3d12.9116583!4d77.651559!16s%2Fg%2F11grqgf_0c",4.2,0,Peter Paul,5.0,7 years ago,2,Response from the owner 6 years ago Thanks Peter ! We are working on our Instore communication :),"Excellent place to source all things organic. Where there is food, cosmetics, clothes or even detergents! Fantastic experience overall. Layout: (5/5) Clear and structured outlet. This is contrary to many other smaller organic outlets in the city which have transformed a room into a store. Here the store must be at least 3000 sq.ft and has a wide aisles and carts to be able to use. Very well lit outlet. Only suggestion is better header cards especially around the powders and staples sections. Got a bit confusing. Product Width: (5/5) This is one of the first organic stores I have seen that also offers clothes and other fair trade items including products of Saahas. Excellent assortment overall. I ended up finding some pukka herbs tea which I have been looking for. Shopping experience: (5/5) As soon as you enter there are plants straight ahead and to the right are the billing sections. Walk in further and the left has cosmetics and the right has tea and cold beverages and items. As you go further in there are clothes, staples and household items. Structured well, but the shopping experience required more time to locate products without clear header cards. The staff were extremely helpful and supported in locating products quickly. Summary: (5/5) Need organic, then look no further. The organic store is the place to come in HSR.",2026-05-11 17:19:21
