Bangalore,The Organic World - Indiranagar,"12th Main, 7th Cross Rd, 7th Cross, HAL 2nd Stage, Indiranagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560008","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+Indiranagar/@12.9704614,77.6450913,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae172ac41b5819:0x11bcd2e9e87bcdc6!8m2!3d12.9704614!4d77.6450913!16s%2Fg%2F11frdzkd5r",4.4,0,,,,0,,"Your one-stop shop for an expansive range of products, from grocery and fresh fruits to home essentials and toiletries. The selection of organic chocolate and snacks, as well as cosmetics and personal care products make for excellent gifting options for the conscious consumer. The prices vary across the range of brands, and you might find offers and sales running occasionally. Very helpful staff, an extensive choice of products and parking around the lane depending on the time of the day make this a must visit for anyone looking at organic produce.",2026-05-11 17:24:19
Bangalore,The Organic World - Indiranagar,"12th Main, 7th Cross Rd, 7th Cross, HAL 2nd Stage, Indiranagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560008","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+Indiranagar/@12.9704614,77.6450913,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae172ac41b5819:0x11bcd2e9e87bcdc6!8m2!3d12.9704614!4d77.6450913!16s%2Fg%2F11frdzkd5r",4.4,0,,,,0,,"I purchased cold pressed sunflower oil and fruits. Organics fruits taste the best. Good quality cold pressed oil too. Timely delivery and even got a free gift from their offer. If you live near indiaranagar double road, highly recommend this place.",2026-05-11 17:24:19
