Bangalore,The Organic World - Indiranagar,"12th Main, 7th Cross Rd, 7th Cross, HAL 2nd Stage, Indiranagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560008","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+Indiranagar/@12.9704614,77.6450913,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae172ac41b5819:0x11bcd2e9e87bcdc6!8m2!3d12.9704614!4d77.6450913!16s%2Fg%2F11frdzkd5r",4.4,0,Damler V,2.0,a year ago,0,"Response from the owner a year ago We are extremely sorry to hear about that experience, Damler V. Rest assured, we have informed the concerned department and they will be looking into what went wrong and how it can be addressed to ensure you have a better experience next time. Thank you for shopping with us. If you can share your contact details with us @(+91 96068 09090) or on hello@theorganicword.com, a team member from Customer Care will be in touch with you at the earliest opportunity to see how best we can resolve this issue. Thank you for contacting The Organic World","Excellent range of quality products and very helpful service in store. Unfortunately, their online shopping portal (website and app) seems to be designed to drive even determined customers away! The website doesn't even allow one to login, because a pin is required, which never reaches your phone. And if you manage to login and fill your shopping cart, you can't check out and pay for it because you can't select a time slot, and the website hangs! Then you have to switch to their phone app, which is slightly better, but that also hangs when you move items from your wishlist into your cart. The search function on both website and app deliver a mixed bag of results, and often items that are available are not displayed! If you manage to place an order, however, the goods will be delivered the next day, though usually with some missing items and without an invoice. Complaints to their customer service elicit the standard reply ""we are working on the issue and will get back to you soon"". Instead of expanding their retail outlets I wish they would focus on fixing their online shopping portal.",2026-05-11 17:23:37
