Bangalore,The Organic World - Indiranagar,"12th Main, 7th Cross Rd, 7th Cross, HAL 2nd Stage, Indiranagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560008","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+Indiranagar/@12.9704614,77.6450913,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae172ac41b5819:0x11bcd2e9e87bcdc6!8m2!3d12.9704614!4d77.6450913!16s%2Fg%2F11frdzkd5r",4.4,0,Sowmya Nivarthi,1.0,2 years ago,1,"Response from the owner 2 years ago We are extremely sorry to hear about that experience, Ms. Sowmya. Rest assured, we have informed the concerned department and they will be looking into what went wrong and how it can be addressed to ensure you have a better experience next time. Thank you for shopping with us. If you can share your contact details with us @(+91 96068 09090) or on hello@theorganicword.com, a team member from Customer Care will be in touch with you at the earliest opportunity to see how best we can resolve this issue. Thank you for contacting The Organic World.","I used to be a loyal patron of this store, but unfortunately, it turned into a huge disappointment. Living in a joint family means we have significant grocery needs, and I always make an effort to buy organic staples(caring health over cost). Initially, the goods' quality seemed satisfactory, but that was short-lived. As time went on, I noticed a steady decline in the quality of the products they offered. To my dismay, the goods I purchased eventually turned out to be infested with pests, rendering them unusable. Seeking resolution, I approached the store's staff for support, but to my dismay, they provided almost no assistance. All I received was a half-hearted apology for the poor quality and a blatantly untrue assurance that things would improve. Despite giving them the benefit of the doubt and waiting for months for any sign of improvement, nothing changed. The store failed to rectify the situation or address the issue adequately. Frustrated and let down, I had no choice but to stop frequenting the store altogether. Instead, I am now forced to look elsewhere to get my organic food staples delivered, which has been an inconvenience. It's disheartening to witness such a decline in a store I once relied on, and their lack of responsibility and action has left a sour taste in my mouth. I sincerely hope they address their shortcomings, but until then, I'll have to rely on other sources to meet my grocery needs.",2026-05-11 17:24:01
