Bangalore,The Organic World - Jayanagar,"37/6, 10th Main Rd, 4th Block, 5th Block, Jayanagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560041","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+Jayanagar/@12.9226217,77.5850677,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae15c52438a1dd:0xead3f9253e1c17d7!8m2!3d12.9226217!4d77.5850677!16s%2Fg%2F11rf84w_qp",4.5,0,meera raman,1.0,4 months ago,0,"Response from the owner 4 months ago We are extremely sorry to hear about that experience, meera raman. We will check the product mentioned to ensure you have a better experience next time. Thank you for shopping with us. If you can share your contact details with us @(+91 96068 09090) or hello@theorganicword.com, we assure you that a team member from Customer Care will be in touch with you at the earliest opportunity","They have good stuff but home delivery when anything has gone bad, they have a very poor replacement system. Rude staff like as if they are doing a favour to us by giving a replacement. Many times we get products that are not good, not fresh and for the prices they charge it is not acceptable. Big basket has a very good system on the other hand. I don't know if it is the organisation policy that needs to be looked at or the training of the staff but not satisfied at all with regards to this. I have raised many complaints earlier but I don't see any resolve. I request the management or looking to it because it reflects very poorly on the company.",2026-05-11 17:35:07
