Bangalore,The Organic World - Kaadubeesanahalli,"Survey No. 16/2, KB Halli, Opposite To Green Elegance,Doddakannelli - Kaadubeesanahalli Rd, Gear School Rd, Devarabisanahalli, Bhoganhalli, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560103","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+Kaadubeesanahalli/@12.9227463,77.6951121,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae134a1c395879:0x866fab275dff1fe2!8m2!3d12.9227463!4d77.6951121!16s%2Fg%2F11vbjx68jl",4.4,0,Roshan Singh,1.0,a year ago,0,"Response from the owner a year ago We are extremely sorry to hear about that experience, Roshan Singh. We will check the product and service concerns mentioned to ensure you have a better experience next time. Thank you for shopping with us. If you can share your contact details with us @(+91 96068 09090) or hello@theorganicword.com, we assure you that a team member from Customer Care will be in touch with you at the earliest opportunity.","Has been a customer for long time but the lack of providing good service to customer is what makine me feel to move away from this shop. Pro: 1) Sometimes seasonal fruits and veggies are really of good quality but as said only sometimes and for same reason looks overpriced as quality should not be compromised if charging more. 2) Onions, Tomato, Garlic and Ginger is always of good quality compare to whats available in market. Cons: 1) If any spoiled item is found it takes forever to return or replace specially mangoes as manager is never to be found on time. And nothing happens without taking manager confirmation. 2) Same goes for any other item. 3) Many times items are not in inventory and you get charged for full amount without discount(as discount shows for item in inventory only) which is happening frequently now a days. 4) One incident where in someone damaged my bike parked in front of shop and ran away and its taking forever for me to chase and get manager for cctv footage as manager here are always away or not available. Incident on 8th April 2025 and manager not to be found till date in shop and is on leave. Not sure if videos can not be checked remotely when timestamp is shared already(lack of basic helping nature) 5) Multiple follow up needs to be done from our side even when we ask them to inform if some items are available in stock. Not sure if they really want to grow or just want to sell stocks to only folks who are coming to store. May be some proactive and enthusiastic work force can help this store to grow but looking at current circumstances it lacks that. Reply to comment (from The Organic World owner) is as below: Talking personally by going to shop itself is not helping how do you think mailing or messaging at customer care or dropping mail to some id will work better ? Count me out from your customer list as every month was spending minimum 5-10K for sure.",2026-05-11 17:37:31
