Bangalore,The Organic World - Sahakar Nagar,"475, 19th Main, 14th Cross Rd, F Block, Sahakar Nagar, Bengaluru, Karnataka 560092","https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Organic+World+-+Sahakar+Nagar/@13.0632171,77.5875601,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x3bae19772045a56d:0x1e42bc522261905f!8m2!3d13.0632171!4d77.5875601!16s%2Fg%2F11yq2vyn_k",4.8,0,,,,0,,"I had an exceptional experience at The Organic World outlet! If you are looking for authentic, high-quality products, this is the place to go. The absolute highlight of my visit was their organic mangoes. They are perfectly ripe, beautifully fragrant, and the taste is just wonderful—a true reminder of how real, chemical-free fruit should taste. Beyond the amazing produce, the staff here deserves a special mention. They are incredibly welcoming, attentive, and genuinely value their customers. It is rare to see such wonderful customer service where the team actively ensures you have a great shopping experience. Highly recommend this outlet for both the fantastic organic food and the warm, helpful team! I will definitely be a returning customer.",2026-05-11 17:51:57
